snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3829 - Iyer Ne Jethalal Ko Kiya Salam?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Jammalamadugu || Something Missamma || Episode 03 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Jammalamadugu Something Missamma Episode 03 MCM

Filmymoji releases its third episode of something Missamma series where on one hand Middle class Madhu reaches Rayalaseema in the lorry he has fallen into and on the other hand Naatu Guntala Gang along with their fathers would be blaming 1A master for taking them to a fake Anjanam practitioner. Inspite of not helping them to find Madhu, Police warn the media people not to put any Ads regarding the missing Madhu case. Failing to publish newspaper Ad, they decide to spread the news through WhatsApp. When they reveal the news to Madhu’s mother she gets really worried and emotional and urges everyone to find and get back her son asap. Madhu gets down from the lorry when it stopped to unload the flower baskets at a marriage function. Madhu meets an opportunist by the name BuggaReddy, who after knowing Madhu’s story leaves him with a suggest to gel along with the marriage party to survive. Madhu gets a lot of chores from a lady called Aandaalu. Suddenly Madhu hears some female’s crying voice. Watch the full episode to find out who the female crying was and would Madhu figures out a way to get away from Rayalaseema.

A young girl named Kaanchi is named a suspect in the murder of two of her family members. Kaanchi is a sweet, seemingly innocent girl who claims to want love and affection from her elders and says she receives hate from them instead. 

Show Name: CID
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1289
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #latestcid 

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXaDflty17VP5hz5qSvqr1I

snippet.title: Marvel Studios' The Marvels | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This fall, The Marvels take flight.

Carol Danvers aka Captain Marvel has reclaimed her identity from the tyrannical Kree and taken revenge on the Supreme Intelligence. But unintended consequences see Carol shouldering the burden of a destabilized universe. When her duties send her to an anomalous wormhole linked to a Kree revolutionary, her powers become entangled with that of Jersey City super-fan, Kamala Khan aka Ms. Marvel, and Carol's estranged niece, now S.A.B.E.R. astronaut Captain Monica Rambeau. Together, this unlikely trio must team-up and learn to work in concert to save the universe as "The Marvels."

Marvel Studios' "The Marvels" stars Brie Larson, Teyonah Parris, Iman Vellani, Zawe Ashton, Gary Lewis, Park Seo-joon, Zenobia Shroff, Mohan Kapur, Saagar Shaikh, and Samuel L. Jackson.

Nia DaCosta directs with Kevin Feige producing. Louis D'Esposito, Victoria Alonso, Mary Livanos, Jonathan Schwartz and Matthew Jenkins serve as executive producers. The screenplay is by Megan McDonnell, Nia DaCosta, Elissa Karasik and Zeb Wells.

Recently, the movie "Oppenheimer" took the internet by storm, captivating audiences worldwide. In a daring and historic experiment, Oppenheimer initiated the detonation of the first nuclear bomb, an event that surpassed all expectations with its resounding success. Yet, this triumph came with a heavy price, as it ushered in a period of profound chaos and uncertainty.Prepare to be engrossed in the captivating narrative of "Oppenheimer" and discover the profound questions it raises about heroism, the consequences of scientific breakthroughs, and the fine line between progress and destruction. snippet.title: Ahmedabad Road Accident: 9 Dead, 13 Injured After Multiple Cars Crash On Ahmedabad’s Iskcon Flyover
snippet.description:
Ahmedabad Road Accident: In a tragic accident nine people have died and 13 others injured in an accident that occurred on Thursday morning on a flyover near ISKCON temple on Sarkhej-Gandhinagar (SG) Highway in Ahmedabad city. Gujarat police described it as a “hit-and-run” involving a “Jaguar” luxury car.

My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3830 | 22 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3830: Car Ki Tamanna
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha, Nattu Kaka, and Bagha have helped Iyer and Babita realize their ambition of purchasing a car. Jetha is pleased when Babita invites Jetha, Champaklal, and Tapu to a special dinner outing. The next morning, Iyer learns from the news that Mumbai may have substantial precipitation in the coming days. Iyer is concerned that the rain may harm their brand-new car, so he parks it in his office space. Babita follows Iyer to his office because she wants to give some rasgullas to Bagha and Nattu Kaka as a mark of appreciation. Meanwhile, the other Gokuldham residents fantasize about getting their own car someday.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3830, 22 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

The highly-anticipated "Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare" features Sandalwood star Rakshit Shetty and is directed by Nithin Krishnamurthy.

snippet.description:
Venkatesh Powerful Court Room Scene | Dharma Chakram Movie | SP Shorts

#DharmaChakram is a 1996 Tollywood film produced by D. Ramanaidu under the #SureshProductions banner, directed by Suresh Krishna. The film stars #Venkatesh in the lead role, #RamyaKrishna as his love interest, and #GirishKarnad as the father and antagonist. The music was composed by M. M. Srilekha. 

#Venkatesh received the Nandi Award for Best Actor and won the Filmfare Best Actor Award (Telugu).

snippet.title: मिश्रण न फेटता ढोकळा | ढोकळा चटणीची सिक्रेट रेसिपी/ सगळीकडून जाळीदार होण्यासाठी 7 टिप्स DhoklaRecipe
snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
सरिताज किचनचे प्रॉडक्ट्स | Saritas Kitchen Products -
 1. सर्व प्रकारची लाकडी घाणा तेलं | All Types of Wood Pressed Oils
 2. डंकावर कुटून केलेला कांदा लसूण मसाला | Handmade Kanda Lasun Masala
 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt
 5. सेंद्रियहळद | Organic Turmeric
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - http://bitly.ws/zDuc
 
मिश्रण न फेटता ढोकळा | ढोकळा चटणीची सिक्रेट रेसिपी/ सगळीकडून जाळीदार होण्यासाठी 7 टिप्स DhoklaRecipe

Ingredients (साहित्य) - 
ढोकळा | ढोकळा रेसिपी | ढोकळा रेसिपी मराठी | झटपट होणारा ढोकळा | बेसन पिठाचा चा ढोकळा | मऊ लुसलुशीत बेसन ढोकळा | खमंग फोडणी दिलेला मऊ ढोकळा | पिवळा ढोकळा | बेसन ढोकळा | Dhokala, Dhokala recipe | Dhokala recipe marathi | Zatpat dhokala | Soft & spongy dhokala | Yellow dhokala | Besan dhokala |

Ingredients (साहित्य) - 
 • तेल - ३ मोठे चमचे  | Oil - 3 tbsp | 9 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • पिठी साखर - ३ मोठे चमचे  | Sugar Powder - 3tbsp | 6 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • लिंबू सत्व - १ १/२ छोटा चमचा | Citric Acid - 1 1/2 tsp | 1 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचा 
 • हिंग - १/४ छोटा चमचा  | Hing - 1/4 tsp 
 • हळद - १/४ छोटा चमचा | Turmeric Powder - 1/4 tsp
 • पाणी - ३ मोठे चमचे | Water 3tbsp | 9 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • बेसन - १ १/२ कप  | 1 1/2 cup
 • पाणी - ३/४ कप | Water 3/4 cup 
 • सोडा - १ १/४ छोटा चमचा | Baking Soda 1 1/4 tsp | 1 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचा 
फोडणी करीता
 • मोहरी - १ छोटा चमचा  | Mustard - 1 tsp
 • तेल - ३ चमचे  | Oil - 3 tsp
 • कडीपत्ता - १० ते १५ पाने | Curry Leaves - 10 to 15 leaves
 • हिरवी मिरची - ३/४  | Green Chilli - 3/4 
 • कोथिंबीर - सजावण्या साठी  | Fresh Coriender 
 • पाणी - १ १/४ कप | Water - 1 1/4 
 • साखर - १ १/४ मोठा चमचा | Sugar - 1 1/4 tbsp
 • मीठ - गरजे नुसार | Salt as per taste 

Dhokala Recipe -  
 • Take oil, sugar Powder, citric Acid, hing, turmeric Powder and water into a mixer jar. Grind all the ingredients well. 
 • Add besan and water then again churn it for some time. 
 • Then grease a tray with little oil & Put some water for boiling into a steamer.
 • Once water is boling add baking soda to the besan mixture & churn the batter for 5-10 Seconds. 
 • Then Pour this batter into the greased tray.
 • Put this tray into a steamer and steam for 15 to 20 minutes. 
 • After 15 to 20 minutes, check if the dhokala is ready using toothpick. 
 • If toothpick comes out clean, it indicates dhokala is cooked completely
 • Take the dhokala out and allow it to cool down completely. 
 • For Tadka, Take a small pan, add oil, mustard, curry leaves, green chillies, sesame for tadka add water, salt and sugar and boil for 2-3 minutes.
 • Cut the dhokla into small pieces & Add the tadka water on top of the ready dhokala . Garnish this with Chopped Fresh coriander.

मिश्रण न फेटता ढोकळा | ढोकळा चटणीची सिक्रेट रेसिपी/ सगळीकडून जाळीदार होण्यासाठी 7 टिप्स DhoklaRecipe

Ingredients (साहित्य) - 
ढोकळा | ढोकळा रेसिपी | ढोकळा रेसिपी मराठी | झटपट होणारा ढोकळा | बेसन पिठाचा चा ढोकळा | मऊ लुसलुशीत बेसन ढोकळा | खमंग फोडणी दिलेला मऊ ढोकळा | पिवळा ढोकळा | बेसन ढोकळा | Dhokala, Dhokala recipe | Dhokala recipe marathi | Zatpat dhokala | Soft & spongy dhokala | Yellow dhokala | Besan dhokala |

Ingredients (साहित्य) - 
 • तेल - ३ मोठे चमचे  | Oil - 3 tbsp | 9 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • पिठी साखर - ३ मोठे चमचे  | Sugar Powder - 3tbsp | 6 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • लिंबू सत्व - १ १/२ छोटा चमचा | Citric Acid - 1 1/2 tsp | 1 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचा 
 • हिंग - १/४ छोटा चमचा  | Hing - 1/4 tsp 
 • हळद - १/४ छोटा चमचा | Turmeric Powder - 1/4 tsp
 • पाणी - ३ मोठे चमचे | Water 3tbsp | 9 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचे 
 • बेसन - १ १/२ कप  | 1 1/2 cup
 • पाणी - ३/४ कप | Water 3/4 cup 
 • सोडा - १ १/४ छोटा चमचा | Baking Soda 1 1/4 tsp | 1 पोहे खाण्याचे चमचा 
फोडणी करीता
 • मोहरी - १ छोटा चमचा  | Mustard - 1 tsp
 • तेल - ३ चमचे  | Oil - 3 tsp
 • कडीपत्ता - १० ते १५ पाने | Curry Leaves - 10 to 15 leaves
 • हिरवी मिरची - ३/४  | Green Chilli - 3/4 
 • कोथिंबीर - सजावण्या साठी  | Fresh Coriender 
 • पाणी - १ १/४ कप | Water - 1 1/4 
 • साखर - १ १/४ मोठा चमचा | Sugar - 1 1/4 tbsp
 • मीठ - गरजे नुसार | Salt as per taste 

Dhokala Recipe -  
 • Take oil, sugar Powder, citric Acid, hing, turmeric Powder and water into a mixer jar. Grind all the ingredients well. 
 • Add besan and water then again churn it for some time. 
 • Then grease a tray with little oil & Put some water for boiling into a steamer.
 • Once water is boling add baking soda to the besan mixture & churn the batter for 5-10 Seconds. 
 • Then Pour this batter into the greased tray.
 • Put this tray into a steamer and steam for 15 to 20 minutes. 
 • After 15 to 20 minutes, check if the dhokala is ready using toothpick. 
 • If toothpick comes out clean, it indicates dhokala is cooked completely
 • Take the dhokala out and allow it to cool down completely. 
 • For Tadka, Take a small pan, add oil, mustard, curry leaves, green chillies, sesame for tadka add water, salt and sugar and boil for 2-3 minutes.
 • Cut the dhokla into small pieces & Add the tadka water on top of the ready dhokala . Garnish this with Chopped Fresh coriander.

snippet.title: Pakistan Army की मेजर है Seema Haider?
snippet.description:
पबजी के जरिए प्रेम होने के बाद पाकिस्तान से अपने बच्चों के साथ अवैध तरीके से भारत पहुंची सीमा हैदर इन दिनों सुर्खियों में हैं. इन सबके बीच सीमा से जुड़े नए-नए दावे भी सोशल मीडिया पर किए जा रहे हैं. कोई सीमा को जासूस बता रहा है तो कोई उसके मुस्लिम होने पर शक जाहिर कर रहा है. सीमा से जुड़ा एक ऐसा ही दावा और है कि वो असल में सीमा नहीं, बल्कि पाकिस्तान आर्मी की मेजर सामिया रहमान हैं और एक खास मकसद से भारत आई हैं.

Poovithal thumbalennil snehamennezhuthi ni
Poomaripolennulil niraye niraye pozhiyunne...
Ramazha chandham neeye ragamay peyyuneee...
Raakaatineenam niyen manavum thanavum nirayunne...
Nenjoramake chayukilee
Nenjudukin thalamay..
kannoramenum theedi nine kankal chimmum neravum.
Eetho niyokam pole iravum pakalum theliyunne...
Niyilla yenkil udalil urukum thiriyonulayunne
(Poovithal...)

Imakal moodum neram mizhi vaathil nii Theliye...
Dhinavum thedunarikee
Pranayam pol neerunne...
Ninavil nirayum nizhale
mazhanoolazhakin oliye...
Ini ee janmam muzhuvan thunnayay nii thudarenam
madhuravasadham nirayum paatin pallavi niyallee..
Pranayasugandham nurayum malaril shalabam njanale..
Nii ragam puthu ragam shruthi cheraamivide...
Nii megam Mazha megam manadharin varamee..
En manasavedhiyiloru nadanathil azhakathu neeyalle.
(Poovithal)


Akamee nirayum puzhanii.. Akathaaril ni ozhukee...
Urukum manamonnivde mazha choodum maruvaay...
Tharalam hridhayam thiraye..thanuvil thazhukum thanu nii..
Pranayam pakarum pen poovonnivide vidarunne..
Anudhinamarikil nira nilavayen innayay neeyileel..
hridhayamudangi ravin madiyil poliyum tharam njan.
Nii thaalam thudi thaalam idanenjin shruthiyee...
Nii moham mazha moham peythozhiyathakame...
Premarthramorathma vipakgika meetamirumey cherumbol { poovithal }

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3829 | 21 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3829: Bazigar Iyer
--------------------------------------------------------
While everyone waits for Iyer to arrive and deliver the good news, Jethalal is worried about losing. Tapu Sena and other members of the society stand to welcome the good news and watch the bet of Jetha and Iyer. Anjali arrives in the society and everyone starts dancing as they thought that Babita and Iyer have brought their car. Champaklal finds out later about Jethalal and Iyer's wager and asks Jetha to enjoy the wager. Who will win this wager? Continue watching to find out what happens next!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3829, 21 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1700000084/bazigar-iyer-1000228692

snippet.title: Robert Downey Jr. & Christopher Nolan Answer The Web's Most Searched Questions | WIRED
snippet.description:
Robert Downey Jr. and director Christopher Nolan from the 2023 film ‘Oppenheimer’ answer their most searched questions from the web. How did Christopher Nolan film a nuclear bomb detonation? How did Robert Downey Jr. become Marvel’s Iron Man? What would an 'Avengers' film directed by Christopher Nolan be like? Watch as they answer these questions and many more.

SAG-AFTRA members are currently on strike; as part of the strike, union actors are not promoting their film and TV projects. This interview was conducted prior to the strike.

snippet.title: Kuki-Zomi Women Lash Out At Government Over Manipur Assault Video
snippet.description:
Manipur Video: People from Kuki-Zomi community gathered at Delhi's Jantar Mantar to protest against the atrocities inflicted on Manipur women after the Manipur assault video, where two Kuki-Zomi women were seen paraded naked and assaulted by a mob of men, went viral. This is what women from Kuki-Zomi community told The Indian Express.

Episode 10: Good News For Reyansh
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Reyansh finds out that Aradhna is single. Later, Aradhna's parents arrive at the temple after Vikram and Pooja's marriage. What will Aradhna do now?. Will this be the start of a relationship between Aradhna and Reyansh? Will they be able to connect with each other? What happens next? Watch the episode to learn more!!

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately puts them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

snippet.description:
ജനസഹസ്രങ്ങൾക്ക് Oommen Chandy ഇനി ദീപ്തമായ ഓർമ്മ. സംസ്കാര ശുശ്രൂഷകൾക്ക് ശേഷം വിങ്ങുന്ന  ഹൃദയവുമായാണ് ജനം Puthuppallyയോട് യാത്ര പറഞ്ഞത്. ഹൃദയത്തോട് ചേർത്തുപിടിച്ചുള്ള പൊതുപ്രവർത്തനത്തിന് ജനഹൃദയങ്ങളിൽ സ്ഥാനമുണ്ടെന്ന്  തെളിയിച്ചാണ്  ഉമ്മൻചാണ്ടിയുടെ നിത്യനിദ്ര.

snippet.title: NEW! Baalveer S3 | Ep 62 | 22 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 62: Kaashvi Learns The Truth
-------------------------------------------------
Baalveer overcomes the giants and attempts to enter the vault, but Maha Mahim Uttan stops him. Kaashvi imagines an exotic city using her skills. Aageel informs Kaashvi that the location she witnessed is known as Shashvan Lok. Kaashvi refuses to believe Aageel's words. Later, Kaashvi finds his parents in that location, which gives her hope, but Aageel informs her that her parents are no longer living. Kaashvi becomes enraged and confronts Aageel about the executioner.

Show Name – Baalveer S3
Star Cast – Dev Joshi, Aditi Sanwal, Ada Khan, Behzaad Khan, Aditya Ranvijay
Episodes No - 62, 22 July 2023
Produced By - Vipul D Shah

#baalveer3  #बालवीर3 #sab 

About the show: 
---------------------------
The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. In this season, Baalveer is stripped of his powers, magic, and memories and lives as a regular boy Veer. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.
